code: @Test public void simpleTestGetMetricInfo() {     String logicalScope = "myService.Status.JVM.ClassLoader".     Map<String, String> variables = new HashMap<>().     variables.put("<A>", "a").     variables.put("<B>", "b").     variables.put("<C>", "c").     String metricName = "ClassesLoaded".     FrontMetricGroup metricGroup = mock(FrontMetricGroup.class, (invocation) -> {         throw new UnsupportedOperationException("unexpected method call").     }).     doReturn(variables).when(metricGroup).getAllVariables().     doReturn(logicalScope).when(metricGroup).getLogicalScope(any(), anyChar()).     MeasurementInfo info = provider.getMetricInfo(metricName, metricGroup).     assertNotNull(info).     assertEquals(String.join("" + MeasurementInfoProvider.SCOPE_SEPARATOR, logicalScope, metricName), info.getName()).     assertThat(info.getTags(), hasEntry("A", "a")).     assertThat(info.getTags(), hasEntry("B", "b")).     assertThat(info.getTags(), hasEntry("C", "c")).     assertEquals(3, info.getTags().size()). }
